# Spotify Clone API - Phase 5 Tests (Search & Player Controls)
# Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### ===== UNIVERSAL SEARCH =====

### Universal search across all entities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Đen&limit=20

### Universal search with specific type
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Lối&type=track&limit=10

### Quick search for autocomplete
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/quick?q=Đen&limit=5

### Get search suggestions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/suggestions?q=Đ&limit=8

### Get trending searches
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/trending?limit=10

### ===== CATEGORY-SPECIFIC SEARCH =====

### Search tracks only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/tracks?q=Lối&limit=15

### Search artists only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/artists?q=Đen&limit=10

### Search albums only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/albums?q=Đen&limit=10

### Search playlists only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/playlists?q=test&limit=10

### ===== PLAYER CONTROLS =====

### Get current playback state (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/player
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Start playback with specific track (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/play
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "track_id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440002",
  "context_type": "album",
  "context_id": "660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440002",
  "position_ms": 0,
  "volume_percent": 80
}

### Pause playback (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/pause
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Resume playback (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/play
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Skip to next track (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/next
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Skip to previous track (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/previous
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Seek to position (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/seek
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "position_ms": 30000
}

### Set volume (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/volume
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "volume_percent": 65
}

### Toggle shuffle on (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/shuffle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "state": true
}

### Set repeat mode (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/repeat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "state": "context"
}

### ===== QUEUE MANAGEMENT =====

### Get current queue (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/queue?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Add track to queue (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/queue
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "track_id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440003",
  "context_type": "album",
  "context_id": "660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440002"
}

### Remove track from queue (requires authentication - replace TOKEN and QUEUE_ITEM_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/queue/QUEUE_ITEM_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Clear entire queue (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/queue
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### ===== DEVICE MANAGEMENT =====

### Transfer playback to different device (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/device
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "device_name": "Mobile App"
}

### Stop playback completely (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/me/player
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### ===== ADVANCED SEARCH SCENARIOS =====

### Empty search query (should return error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=

### Very long search query (should return error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=this_is_a_very_long_search_query_that_exceeds_the_maximum_allowed_length_for_search_terms_and_should_return_an_error

### Search with special characters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Đức Phúc

### Search with numbers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=2024

### Case insensitive search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=ĐEN

### Partial match search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search?q=Lối C

### ===== PLAYER EDGE CASES =====

### Try player actions without authentication
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/player

### Try to play invalid track ID (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/play
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "track_id": "invalid-track-id"
}

### Try to seek to invalid position (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/seek
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "position_ms": -1000
}

### Try to set invalid volume (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/volume
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "volume_percent": 150
}

### Try to set invalid repeat state (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/repeat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "state": "invalid_state"
}

### ===== INTEGRATION SCENARIOS =====

### Start playback from album context (requires authentication - replace TOKEN)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/play
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "track_id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440002",
  "context_type": "album",
  "context_id": "660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440002"
}

### Search and play from search results
GET http://localhost:3000/api/search/tracks?q=Lối&limit=1

### Then play the first result (copy track_id from above)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/me/player/play
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "track_id": "TRACK_ID_FROM_SEARCH_RESULT",
  "context_type": "search",
  "context_id": "Lối"
}

